“I’m just a fan”.

Whenever I see these scenes I think about how Eve probably watched and read a lot of True Crime stories at a very early age and started taking notes about her favorite cases and had literal journals about them with all kinds of data and pictures and drawings and now she has extended her interest to Villanelle, who she hasn’t met yet here, with a complete different goal and it’s so… much lmao fdgsfjdsjfdh.
